comments: [1] w/Clarence Clemons on sax ; [2] w/Baba Olatunji, Sikiru Adepoju and Kitaro, Recorded fanfare and NYE Countdown before Sugar Magnolia ; [3] Usually, after the pause before SSDD (whether it follows Sugar Magnolia or another song) there is a single note, then a few beats of silence, then the lyrics begin."Sunshine daydream."  In this one there is a three minute Sugar Magnolia Jam after the Dew and before the pause and then the start of SSDD.
